OL,3,CPembrokeshire Council says it won't
OL,4,Cintroduce tourism tax for at least two
OL,5,Cyears
OL,7,FIf all councils introduced it, it
OL,8,Fcould generate up to #33m a year.
OL,10,FMark Drakeford has previously said
OL,11,Fthat he does not think that any
OL,12,Fcouncil in Wales could bring in the
OL,13,Flevy before 2027.
OL,15,FNow, the deputy leader of
OL,16,FPembrokeshire Council, Paul Miller,
OL,17,Fhas confirmed his administration will
OL,18,Fnot be introducing the levy during
OL,19,Fthis council term. The next election
OL,20,Fis due to be held in May 2027.
